<template>
   <!-- Default makes items selectable (one at a time) -->
    <vue3-tree-vue :items="items" 
                   :isCheckable="false"
                   :hideGuideLines="false"
                   v-model:selectedItem="selectedItem">
      
    </vue3-tree-vue>
</template>

export default {

 

  data() {
    return {
     treeViewItem : '',
     selectedItem:[],
     items:[

      "name": "Rejection Emails",

      "type": "emails",

                        "name": "Solved Problems (30)",

                    {

    {

          {
            "name": "Space Station Design",

          }
      ]
    }
  ]
    }
  },
  created() {
   
  
  },
};
</script>
